From 4ad61c7a7857589d1db0e0d9dc302e609e4839d5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Daniel Micay <danielmicay@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 26 Aug 2017 20:16:03 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 073/103] Revert "mm: revert x86_64 and arm64 ELF_ET_DYN_BASE
 base changes"

This reverts commit aab425db4279aeb83b7911693f0cccbd3644c9fd.
---
 arch/arm64/include/asm/elf.h | 8 ++------
 arch/x86/include/asm/elf.h   | 4 ++--
 2 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)

